leted<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<h4>v1.04 - October 12, 2016<\\/h4>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Add logic to stop scheduled events when the form action logic is not met<\\/li>\\n<li>Automatically update the queue times when an entry is updated<\\/li>\\n<li>Only show countdown on the debug queue if the trigger will be happening within the next 3 days<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<h4>v1.03 - October 11, 2016<\\/h4>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Use repeat settings to calculate next date if a past date is selected. If date has passed, and the action shouldn\'t repeat, skip it.<\\/li>\\n<li>Add frm_autoresponder_time hook to set the time attached to a date field. Defaults to midnight in the site timezone.<\\/li>\\n<li>Add security to ajax actions<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix autoupdates<\\/li>\\n<li>Prevent sending when date field is empty<\\/li>\\n<li>Prevent infinite loop if 0 is selected for time interval<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\",\"plugin\":\"formidable-autoresponder\\/formidable-autoresponder.php\",\"icons\":{\"1x\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/icon-256x256.png\"},\"banners\":{\"high\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/banner-1544x500.png\",\"low\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/banner-1544x500.png\"}},\"168072\":{\"title\":\"Formidable API\",\"name\":\"Formidable API\",\"slug\":\"formidable-api\",\"version\":\"1.07\",\"new_version\":\"1.07\",\"location\":[\"fp.strategy11.com\\/releases\\/formidable-api\\/formidable-api-1.07.zip\"],\"excerpt\":\"Send submissions to other sites with REST APIs including from one Formidable Forms site to another. Add a full forms API for forms, form fields, views, and entries.\",\"id\":168072,\"released\":\"2016-11-02 00:00:00\",\"categories\":[\"Business\",\"Strategy11\"],\"docs\":\"\\/knowledgebase\\/formidable-api\\/\",\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/formidableforms.com\\/downloads\\/formidable-api\\/\",\"changelog\":\"<h4>v1.07 - December 26, 2018<\\/h4>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Fix: multiple files were not correctly attached to the created entry<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: when a file was created via the API, it was being duplicated on the receiving end<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: When the API plugin is active, and Formidable is not, there was an error when creating a new page with the new WP editor<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<h4>v1.06 - October 8, 2018<\\/h4>\\n<ul>\\n<li>New: Add image importing via the REST API. Now an image can be uploaded from another site when the URL is included in the API request.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Prevent CORS error with ajax calls. This resolves issues with double submissions, redirecting with validation errors, and adding rows in a repeater.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: The returned form object was different after a form was edited than after create or get.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<h4>v1.05.01 - August 22, 2018<\\/h4>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Fix issue with file fields not saving the received value<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<h4>v1.05 - July 27, 2018<\\/h4>\\n<ul>\\n<li>New: Add start_date and end_date parameters to filter the route to get entries<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Add better functionality to the search parameter in the route to get entries<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Allow the registration validation to trigger during API call<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: reCaptcha was returning an error when creating an entry<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Creating an entry that included dynamic fields was causing a fatal error by using deprecated functions<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: The route to create a form wasn\'t working correctly<\\/li>\\n<li>Remove old sslverify =&gt; false lines since they are no longer recommended<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<h4>v1.04 - April 5, 2018<\\/h4>\\n<ul>\\n<li>New: Allow entry keys in routes like frm\\/v2\\/entries\\/#<\\/li>\\n<li>New: Allow form key in frm\\/v2\\/forms\\/#\\/entries<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Correctly update entries with repeating and embedded forms<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Correctly update an entry with a date when the date format is something other than Y-d-m<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Correctly process wp shortcodes in [shortcode]content[\\/shortcode] format when preparing the outbound API form action<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Remove the DELETE routes for frm\\/v2\\/entries and frm\\/v2\\/forms\\/#\\/entries. These didn\'t have any functionality behind them.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Return a better response when an entry isn\'t found with frm\\/v2\\/entries\\/#<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Correct the nonce values when creating and updating entries so it won\'t block submissions<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\",\"plugin\":\"formidable-api\\/formidable-api.php\",\"icons\":{\"1x\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/icon-256x256.png\"},\"banners\":{\"high\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/banner-1544x500.png\",\"low\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/banner-1544x500.png\"}},\"20834175\":{\"title\":\"Formidable Payments\",\"name\":\"Formidable Payments\",\"slug\":\"formidable-payments\",\"version\":\"1.14\",\"new_version\":\"1.14\",\"location\":[\"fp.strategy11.com\\/releases\\/payments\\/formidable-payments-1.14.zip\"],\"excerpt\":\"\",\"id\":20834175,\"released\":\"2018-11-06 12:08:25\",\"categories\":[],\"docs\":\"\",\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/formidableforms.com\\/downloads\\/formidable-payments\\/\",\"changelog\":\"\",\"plugin\":\"\",\"icons\":{\"1x\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/icon-256x256.png\"},\"banners\":{\"high\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/banner-1544x500.png\",\"low\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/banner-1544x500.png\"}},\"93790\":{\"title\":\"Formidable Pro\",\"name\":\"Formidable Pro\",\"slug\":\"formidable-pro\",\"version\":\"3.06.04\",\"new_version\":\"3.06.04\",\"location\":[\"fp.strategy11.com\\/releases\\/formidable-pro-3.06.04.zip\"],\"excerpt\":\"\",\"id\":93790,\"released\":\"2010-02-01 16:27:26\",\"categories\":[\"Personal\",\"Strategy11\"],\"docs\":\"\",\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/formidableforms.com\\/downloads\\/formidable-pro\\/\",\"changelog\":\"<h4>v3.06.04 - April 3, 2019<\\/h4>\\n<ul>\\n<li>New: Add option to use [date offset=\\\"+3 days\\\"] in the default value. Instead of only showing the current date using [date], a custom date can be used with any of the strtotime functions that date filters in views use.<\\/li>\\n<li>New: Allow RTE fields in conditional logic.<\\/li>\\n<li>Move the message for the logs add-on inside of the form actions that use it.<\\/li>\\n<li>New: Automatically remove any HTML used inside the frm-math shortcode for more flexibility.<\\/li>\\n<li>New: Use the edit entry link in the admin bar to make it more clear where a post can be edited. This link is changed when the post content is generated from the view, and editing the post wouldn\'t have any effect.<\\/li>\\n<li>Tweak: Only check for required fields before uploading a file on the first page of the form, rather than checking for required fields on every page.<\\/li>\\n<li>Added usage tracking. This will allow us to simplify settings in a future release and better cater to the majority of use cases.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: During import, forms with a page break were losing the logged in and edit settings.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<h4>v3.06.03 - March 19, 2019<\\/h4>\\n<ul>\\n<li>New: Improved form builder education and workflows: install and activate add-ons without ever leaving the form builder and form settings page!<\\/li>\\n<li>A cookie was being created after each form submission. Now, a cookie is only created if the form includes the option to limit the form by cookie.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: The histogram graph type now works correctly.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: When using conditional logic with a user ID field, process the \'Current user\' selection correctly.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Admins were not allowed to create a second entry in the backend for a form limited to one per user when editing entries was disabled.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: A dropdown field with a read-only value was not being used in calculations if the field also has conditional logic.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<h4>v3.06.02 - March 6, 2019<\\/h4>\\n<ul>\\n<li>New: Show a message to make it clear when pro is installed but not active.<\\/li>\\n<li>New: Add \'Expiration\' into the credit card display value<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Clear the slider field value when it is conditionally hidden so calculations will be accurate.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Remove the HTML5 required attribute in conditionally hidden fields from v3.06.01. This was causing issues in some cases.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: When a multiselect field is hidden with conditional logic, don\'t automatically select a default value.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: When an entry with a dynamic field is edited, include the options for the original user when the options are limited to those the user created.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<h4>v3.06.01 - February 21, 2019<\\/h4>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Notice: The nested Pro and Lite version has been discontinued. If you were still running a single plugin for both of these versions, you will see a link after update to install the Pro version again. There should be two Formidable plugins: Formidable Forms and Formidable Forms Pro.<\\/li>\\n<li>Notice: The default HTML for field types with multiple inputs now use div instead of label for the field label for WCAG compliance. This will only affect new fields.<\\/li>\\n<li>New: Better WCAG compliance. Added aria-required to required fields and aria-invalid when javascript validation is turned on. Remove the required attribute when a field is conditionally hidden.<\\/li>\\n<li>New: Add an empty line to separate repeater content in email notifications and an hr after each block of fields in a repeater using the default format<\\/li>\\n<li>New: Save the toggle off value in the field instead of a blank field<\\/li>\\n<li>New: Create an index.php file in the folders where files are uploaded for added security<\\/li>\\n<li>Update Chosen script<\\/li>\\n<li>Remove the checkbox to toggle a repeater. Add a repeater field directly instead of switching back and forth.<\\/li>\\n<li>Use en for the default datepicker locale instead of blank to simplify multilingual sites<\\/li>\\n<li>Add functions to get a list of field strings to translate for multilingual add-ons. This will make maintaining strings much easier without a delay.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: A CSV export with a field with separate values inside a repeater was showing \'Array\'<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Position the inline repeater buttons correctly when the default label position is top with field settings using \'inside\'<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: error message was appearing for conditionally hidden required address fields inside a repeater.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<h4>v3.06 - January 30, 2019<\\/h4>\\n<ul>\\n<li>New: Add one-click form creation from a form template and adjust the way a new form is created.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Prevent the \'Advanced\' section from hiding in non-Formidable blocks.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Some users were seeing PHP error messages in PHP 5.2 and 5.3.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Submit Button Logic wasn\'t consistently showing Dynamic fields in the conditions.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Prevent jQuery UI CSS from loading on the builder page from the Datepicker Options add-on. This was causing the icons and other link text to use the wrong colors with some jQuery themes.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\",\"plugin\":\"formidable-pro\\/formidable-pro.php\",\"icons\":{\"1x\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/icon-256x256.png\"},\"banners\":{\"high\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/banner-1544x500.png\",\"low\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/banner-772x250.png\"}},\"19366995\":{\"title\":\"Formidable Pro Business Package\",\"name\":\"Formidable Pro Business Package\",\"slug\":\"formidable-pro-small-business-package\",\"version\":\"\",\"new_version\":\"\",\"location\":[],\"excerpt\":\"\",\"id\":19366995,\"released\":\"2017-09-01 12:09:09\",\"categories\":[\"Strategy11\"],\"docs\":\"\",\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/formidableforms.com\\/downloads\\/formidable-pro-small-business-package\\/\",\"changelog\":\"\",\"plugin\":\"\",\"icons\":{\"1x\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/icon-256x256.png\"},\"banners